summary: This is an email exchange from July 2021 between an FBI Special Agent in the New York Office's Child Exploitation and Human Trafficking Task Force and an external correspondent. The external party apologizes for failing to follow up on 'Maxwell questions' and attempts to schedule a call to discuss them.
